stein: This is a Stein configuration file
title: Latency test: 7 millions flights (PC ONLY)
description: In the next steps, you will be asked to perform some operations on the visual interface, representing data on about 7 millions flights, and to answer some general questions and other questions linked to the perceived latency of the visual system (i.e, how much time was required in order to update the visual components after you did an interaction with it?)
